Luxury watches fascinate us.Watch enthusiasts inspire us.Discover more about
Chrono24.

COMPANY

   People who love luxury watches inspire us as much as precious
   timepieces. That’s why sellers and buyers of luxury watches have our
   undivided attention.

   We know that our company wouldn’t exist without valuable watches and
   enthusiastic watch lovers. But we are not only fond of high-quality
   timepieces and their admirers. The complexities of information
   technology and the challenges of global markets also motivate us to
   push ourselves further every day. Because web and mobile technologies
   are our core competencies.
   Global Player

GLOBAL PLAYER

   The luxury watch market is global. Chrono24 provides easy, safe, and
   reliable market access to all watch enthusiasts.

MISSION

   There is something that propels us forward. An idea that we pursue in
   full stride. Our long-term goal for Chrono24.
   Facts & Figures

FACTS & FIGURES

   Watches and Internet – a fantastic combination of tradition and
   high-tech. Endless possibilities that inspire us to excel every day.
   LEARN MORE

TEAM

   What sets us apart? An inspiring corporate culture, an experienced
   management team, and the contagious team spirit in our units.

CULTURE

   Our goal is to bring trust and transparency to the global luxury watch
   market. This is also reflected in our corporate culture.

MANAGEMENT

   Aside from a love for watches, our management team brings years of
   experience in successfully operating online marketplaces to the table.

UNITS

   Each of our units is unique, but all share one thing: people who are
   passionate about their work.

    1.
    2.
    3.

   Team Culture

   Content employees create the best products. Openness and appreciation
   are key elements of our corporate culture.

   Valuable watches and enthusiastic watch lovers – a fascinating global
   market for our company.

   Chrono24 is a dynamic company. We scrutinize structures, dare to do
   things differently, and create our own future.
