Always a step ahead of the times.

GLOBAL PLAYER

   BOUGHT IN NEW YORK. SOLD IN TOKYO.

   Trustworthy processing, secure transactions, and transparent services –
   that's why Chrono24 is known and loved worldwide. Watch lovers will
   find exactly what they're looking for: luxury watches of all kinds.

MARKETPLACE

   Chrono24 has been the global online marketplace for luxury watches
   since 2003. We are the number one address for luxury watches for
   commercial watch dealers and private sellers from around the world.
   Marketplace

INVESTORS

   In terms of finances, our company is excellently positioned. Well-known
   investors trust in our performance and invest in our future. Just
   recently, Insight Ventures contributed a total of 21 million euros.
   Investors

FACTS AND FIGURES

   IMPRESSIVE NUMBERS

   On Chrono24, more than 10,000 professional dealers and private sellers
   from over 90 countries offer more than 300,000 watches. With content in
   22 languages, our website attracts more than 350,000 visitors every
   day. Over 2 million users have already downloaded the Chrono24 apps for
   iOS and Android.
   Impressive Numbers

   On Chrono24, you can find more than 300,000 watches with a total value
   of 2.5 billion euros. In 2015, watches worth about 700 million euros
   were sold through Chrono24.

MISSION

   THE HOME OF LUXURY WATCH BUYERS

   Our mission is to offer luxury watch buyers all over the world a
   platform that feels just as good as their own home – or even better.
   Our aim is to offer the very best in terms of security, trust, and
   comfort. We’re fully dedicated to our customers in order to become not
   only the largest online marketplace for luxury watches worldwide, but
   also the most appealing. Your personal favorite when it comes to
   information, transaction, and service in all matters concerning luxury
   watches. Or as we say at Chrono24: “The Home of Luxury Watch Buyers”.

WE ARE GROWING. GROW WITH US!

