Runs like clockwork.

OUR CULTURE

   WATCHES, PEOPLE, AND IT

   Openness, appreciation, and personal responsibility are core values at
   Chrono24. Our team includes experts as well as unconventional thinkers.
   Different types of people, who love challenges. Our employees from 14
   countries form an international team and a strong community.

MANAGEMENT TEAM

   TALK IS SILVER. ACTION IS GOLDEN.

   The Chrono24 management team includes entrepreneurs who have almost 20
   years of experience in building successful Internet companies and
   managers who not only have a theoretical grasp of their work, but are
   also experts in practice.

TIM STRACKE

   co-CEO & Founder

   Tim is our strategist and the driving force for new business. He gives
   us perspective and clarity with his keen eye for numbers and facts.

HOLGER FELGNER

   co-CEO

   Holger has set his sights on scaling Chrono24 for an international
   market. His vast experience with growing companies is the perfect
   foundation for our continued success.

SVEN HIMMELSBACH

   COO

   Sven is where strategic planning meets our daily business. He ensures
   that we tackle the right projects at the right time.

MICHAEL KRKOSKA

   CTO & Founder

   Michael is the technical master watchmaker behind Chrono24. He hones
   the technology and keeps the wheels turning, because he knows each one
   of them.

DIRK SCHWARTZ

   Founder & Advisor

   Dirk has the vision and leads the way. He shapes the evolution of
   Chrono24 and drives us forward through his intuition and passion.

